title: A Tribute to Van Halen 2000 mp3 192ak
description:
This is the tribute album dedicated to Van Halen released in 2000 . They were attended by the major artists of the heavy metal of the period. And I even stuck a real one in.

1.Unchained (3:23)
   
2.I'm The One (3:39)

4.Light Up The Sky (3:48)
   
5.Panama (3:25)
   
6.Hot For Teacher (4:42)
 
7.Running With The Devil (3:42)
   
8.(Oh) Pretty Woman (3:03)
   
9.Atomic Punk (3:36)
    
10.So This Is Love (3:11)
    
11.Little Guitars (4:48)  
 
12.Hear About It Later (4:35)
